{"type": "article", "id": 23275, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-03-04T07:30:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 1954, "name": "包装"}, {"id": 3208, "name": "Normann Copenhagen"}, {"id": 24380, "name": "Mosaico+ t"}, {"id": 24381, "name": "Stitch Design Co."}, {"id": 24382, "name": "Simon Legald"}, {"id": 24383, "name": "Nathalie Teugels"}, {"id": 24384, "name": "Sylvain Aebischer"}, {"id": 24385, "name": "Alexander Main"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 54, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110758XpVtlEIdum0yRGYe.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>Too Clothes Rack Small grey by Simon Legald &amp; Normann Copenhagen </h2>\n<p>这是北欧家具品牌 Normann Copenhagen 联合设计师 Simon Legald 推出的晾衣杆。用橡木条做结构搭建出三角空间，上面是挂衣服铁杆，下面连接了带孔的平台，可以放上包和鞋帽。晾衣杆在设计上没有多余的部分，简洁干净，能适应任何环境。有黑白两种选择，大小型号分别宽 74cm、120cm ，售价 374 美元起，<a href=\"http://www.normann-copenhagen.com/products/toj-clothes-rack-small?v=600015\">这里是购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170702eG0KdpUQ4u9FLNsD.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170703YAR6JKkhQ28cgeGV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170703Cxbh7yWwKvnofXgJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170704cx9h02WQyI8TPVZi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170704x1lXvs7aR0MqEwQb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021707054yY0oPkGFBVcHmdX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>moov by Nathalie Teugels</h2>\n<p>这是一把可以为手机充电的椅子，名字“moov”就是移动（move）的意思。椅子的外形很简单，由榉木和悬臂钢架组成。荷兰设计师 Nathalie Teugels 利用了压电效应，在椅子上安装传感器，当人坐在椅子上或者移动椅子，就能激活传感器发电。蓝色的悬臂也是 USB 接口，直接连接到手机上充电。<a href=\"http://nteugels.tumblr.com/prototype\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170705kpZdbgXj5O0MHycV.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170706gw6NSlWGTDXPt7MB.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170706wVTPnYBb0XNQId2G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170707CH0vq6hZ5Il3rycb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170707IpAGm0qrUQu8yOC6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.12591687\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<h2>Crack by Sylvain Aebischer</h2>\n<p>巴黎设计师 Sylvain Aebischer 利用开裂的旧木梁做了一组存钱罐。每一个存钱罐都是边长为 10 厘米的立方体，裂口成为投放硬币的口，很有隐蔽性。木材的天然纹路让这组存钱罐有了令人熟悉的手工感，是一个不错的废物利用的想法。每个存钱罐的纹路都不一样，可以购买，<a href=\"http://www.sylvainaebischer.ch/v2/spip.php?page=rubrique&amp;id_rubrique=6&amp;lang=en\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170708yYUenmwZhlfEQTsG.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170708CXtIrAhdLQcy3ZY0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170709mi9PECxqDj0bNnRM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.784375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170709GiNySxTYKQl5cXz8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Africa Now by Mosaico+ t</h2>\n<p>意大利品牌 Mosaico+ t 最新推出的是 Africa Now 系列，运用了如粉和黑、银和黑搭配的颜色，具有极大的视觉对比，让人想起非洲织物上的图案。在这种颜色搭配的基础上，组合了具有几何感的图案，比如 Pivot 使用边长为 15 毫米的瓷砖，排列出的效果更有冲击力。而 Twist 的宽度有 20 毫米，光泽更低，也更柔和。<a href=\"http://www.mosaicopiu.it/it/articolo/africa-now\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170710iomUhgs81v7rWe5D.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.30479103\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170710CNje2kPJfSou4rpI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170711JSqvruT1Q9V8KZym.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021707116zfgmwk8B2bLPnjA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170712TtpXZ8aY01r27uck.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Solly’s lamp by Alexander Main</h2>\n<p>这是一盏极为简化的灯，它近似一个圆筒一样的水杯，上面连接的手提带增加了它的便捷性。这盏灯通过太阳能发电，而可触式玻璃才是它真正的开关。灯的下面其实是一个音响，灯内的蓝牙系统可以连接到手机 app 以播放音乐。产品目前还是一个概念，<a href=\"http://alexandermain.com/#/sollys/\">这里是更多信息</a>。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170712x8MCbIdyBz0RHkpe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170713IGbRFyvZE2n9gr6f.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170713rPcV6gsJ7U1N4x5i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170714LFKonu4O2g0YZ7PW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170714s37CIFP6AdjHKm5a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>SIDESHOW PRESS CANDLE by Stitch Design Co.</h2>\n<p>当你不知道送什么礼物给别人时，蜡烛也许是个不错的选择。这组蜡烛采用立方体盒子式的包装，盖子下面露出了里面盒子的彩色的边，是不完全遮盖的，有点引人揭开它的感觉。彩色的边对应了里面放蜡烛的杯子的颜色，对比带有简单文字的白色“外罩”，显得更纯粹。盒子上的文字是居中排布，普兰、桃红和墨绿这三种选色都很清新淡雅。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170715HE3unjVbq4eUxISZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170715wmxEdhVr3J8aGgFl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170716zb2Vwc8MCKQTevWk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170716NL7I1sOf6B2KTjRl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170717ioe4BbyjRgzqFKpL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170717GEA7UrLfTJdb8MmF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}